Natividad Vacío https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natividad_Vac%C3%ADo 0 Natividad Vacío (September 8, 1912 – May 30, 1996) was an American character actor in films and television from the 1950s through the 1980s. Born Natividad Domínguez Vacío in El Paso, Texas, he was Mexican American. He nearly always played a Hispanic character in his 65 film and television appearances. He was married to Henriqueta (Queta) Vacío. Natividad_Vacío ( September_8_,_1912 – May_30_,_1996 ) was an_American_character_actor in films and television from the_1950s through the_1980s .
